congregation for the doctrine of the fai.data-term: congregation for the doctrine of the faith

examples.en: There's no need to conduct an inquisition about so trivial a matter.
I had to face a two-hour inquisition from my parents about where I'd been.
During the Inquisition, the torturers would stretch their victims on a rack.
His political enemies were conducting an inquisition into the details of his personal life.
